{"tid":1034821,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"法甲球星麥巴比向勒邦占士妙傳入樽","createTime":"2019-02-24T07:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T12:04:28.000Z","uid":199292,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e4b57c1416787b25c76f9c640679ccaede970ddb","tid":1034821,"uid":199292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T07:59:01.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xYleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=af9d3323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】基利安麥巴比成為45年來首位在頭18場轟入19球的球員，寫下歷史。<br />\n前鋒基利安麥巴比（Kylian Mbappe）在周日法甲，下半場抽入靚窩利，<span style=\"color: red;\">帶領巴黎聖日耳門作客以1:0擊敗聖人難忘的畫面就是在第3節，向勒邦占士（LeBron James）交出彈籃板的妙傳，讓大帝後上雙手入樽，力度大得差點鋤爆玻璃，看得球迷熱血沸騰。 兩人在熱火共事了4個球季，攜手贏得2次總冠軍，感情一直非常好。熱火也在twitter上載了這個入球的片段，留言說：「這是最後一次。」 韋迪跟40歲的奴域斯基皆最後一次出戰明星賽，因此在第3節後，現場播放了向這2名老將致敬的片段，他們亦獲贈送印有名字的紀念明星賽球衣反留念，在熱鬧之中也有一幕感人場面。 至於跟占士在2015/16球季合作，經典地反勝勇士捧走總冠軍的艾榮，同樣跟前隊友再來一記拆你屋；艾榮鏟籃後，傳予身旁的大帝爆樽。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/hk.sports.yahoo.com/amphtml/news/%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E6%25AF%259419%25E7%2590%2583%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2-%25E7%25B4%2580%25E9%258C%2584%25E5%25A5%25BD-%25E7%2590%2583%25E9%259A%258A%25E6%259B%25B4%25E5%25A5%25BD-070308834--spt.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fhk.sports.yahoo.com%2Famphtml%2Fnews%2F%2525E9%2525BA%2525A5%2525E5%2525B7%2525B4%2525E6%2525AF%25259419%2525E7%252590%252583%2525E5%252589%2525B5%2525E6%2525AD%2525B7%2525E5%25258F%2525B2-%2525E7%2525B4%252580%2525E9%25258C%252584%2525E5%2525A5%2525BD-%2525E7%252590%252583%2525E9%25259A%25258A%2525E6%25259B%2525B4%2525E5%2525A5%2525BD-070308834--spt.html&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xYleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=39f8296f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.